        <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">mice</ENAMEX> died). 
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">RCA</ENAMEX> values for the <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">K1</NUMEX>-specific phage
