        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">environment</ENAMEX>).
        <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>) The <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Phage Replication Assay</ENAMEX> (PRA) provides a simple
        measure of the rate of replication (and host cell killing)
        of lytic phage under defined conditions. By varying those
