          measured in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LB</ENAMEX> and in <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">mouse serum</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Assays</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LB</ENAMEX> were
